# AGENTS.md Project-Root Manifest Spec

## Core Requirements
- **setup**: 
  - `init`: `npx create-cex-agent @aaif/openai`
  - `deps`: `npm install --save-dev eslint prettier`
  - `lint`: `npx eslint --ext .ts,.tsx src/`
  - `format`: `npx prettier --write src/`

- **test**: 
  - `unit`: `jest --config jest.config.ts`
  - `e2e`: `cypress run --config-file cypress.config.ts`

- **deploy**: 
  - `prod`: `npm run build && firebase deploy`
  - `stage`: `npm run build -- --stage`

## PR Format
- **title**: `[feat]`/`[fix]`/`[docs]` + brief description
- **body**: 
  - `:bug: Fix bug in X`
  - `:tada: Add new feature Y`
  - `:memo: Update documentation`
- **footer**: `Fixes #123`/`Closes #456`

## Coding Conventions
- **agent**: 
  - `@type`: `openai`/`anthropic`/`google`
  - `@model`: `gpt-4`/`claude-2`/`gemini-pro`
  - `@tokens`: `4096`/`2048`/`8192`
- **prompt**: 
  - `@format`: `json`/`yaml`/`text`
  - `@schema`: `https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema`
- **security**: 
  - `@rate_limit`: `1000`/`5000`/`10000`
  - `@auth`: `oauth2`/`api-key`/`none`
